+2. Edit `intake_watcher.py` to include the new prompt in its processing pipeline.
+3. Update `planner.py` to incorporate the new prompt into its DAG.
+4. Run `prompt_factory.py` to generate a new prompt factory instance with the updated configuration.
+5. Deploy the new build using Vercel.
+
